  title="Free Multiplayer Browser Games — Play Online With Friends | Weekly Arcade"
  metaDescription="Play free multiplayer browser games online with friends — no downloads, no signup. Drawing party games, racing, chess, and sports with real-time competition and global leaderboards."
  keywords="free multiplayer browser games, multiplayer games online, play with friends online free, online multiplayer games no download, browser multiplayer games, free online games with friends, drawing game multiplayer"
  h1="Free Multiplayer Browser Games"
  introText="Play <strong>free multiplayer browser games</strong> with friends or compete against players worldwide. Drawing party games, real-time racing, strategic chess, and competitive sports — all running in your browser with no downloads and no signup required."
  seoHeading="Play Free Multiplayer Games Online"
  seoText="Weekly Arcade's multiplayer games connect you with players worldwide through real-time WebSocket competition and global leaderboards. From party drawing games to competitive racing, every multiplayer game supports up to 30 players per room, loads in under 1.5 seconds, and works on any device including mobile. Signed-in players who compete on leaderboards play 3x more sessions than guests."
  seoBullets={[
    '<strong>Party drawing game</strong> — Draw fast, guess faster in <a href="/games/doodle-dash/">Doodle Dash</a> with Speed Draw mode — up to 30 players drawing simultaneously',
    '<strong>3D racing multiplayer</strong> — Drift and compete on 15 tracks in <a href="/games/drift-legends/">Drift Legends</a> with real-time opponents via WebSocket',
